name: Chubby Shoe vs Joe Star
description: Me and my best friend Joe Star are the best pair ever and we both love being Youtubers. Now it is time to prove who would win in a Youtuber battle. To make things easy for Joe Star he gets an army and I only get you, the player. You need to get the key and kill Joe Star. Hey Joe Star, I bet you can't make a video game as good as mine. Maybe  you can but prove it; I dare you. But I hope this game is fun.
